title: 2021 Week 5 Preview FROM LONDON
itunes:title: 2021 Week 5 Preview FROM LONDON
description:
A hotel room filled with some heroes - Dan Hanzus, Gregg Rosenthal and Erica Tamposi are extremely jet lagged after their flight to London. Sky sports Neil Reynolds join them to preview some of the primetime games and Gregg issues an apology for something he said years ago.
